'''Mass structure''' is a [[structure]], natural or manufactured, that is made by piling up of materials.<ref>[http://schools.cbe.ab.ca/b682/pdfs/Science%207/Structures%20and%20Forces%20T1-2.pdf Structures and Forces]</ref>

Examples of mass structures include [[pyramids]], [[igloos]], and [[beaver dams]].

