blisher=[[Springer Science & Business Media]] |location=Berlin |isbn=3-540-03875-2 |id={{ISBN|978-3-540-03875-7}}. {{LIBRIS|5362583}}}} (NB. A rewrite of the earlier "''Electric Contacts Handbook''".)</ref> <ref name="R5">{{cite web |title=Holm-samlingen |language=Swedish |trans-title=The Holm Collection |date=2010-06-05 |publisher={{ill|Library of the Royal Institute of Technology|sv|Kungliga Tekniska Högskolans Biblioteket}} (KTHB) |url=http://www.lib.kth.se/main/holm-samlingen.asp |access-date=2018-05-28 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100212023232/http://www.lib.kth.se/main/holm-samlingen.asp |archive-date=2010-02-12}}</ref> <ref name="R6">{{cite web |title=The IEEE Holm Conference on Electrical Contact - Ragnar Holm Scientific Achievement Award |publisher=[[IEEE]] - Components, Packaging, and Manufacturing Technology Society (CPMT) |date=2010-06-05 |url=http://www.ewh.ieee.org/soc/cpmt/tc1/HolmAwards.html |access-date=2018-05-28 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528175400/http://www.ewh.ieee.org/soc/cpmt/tc1/HolmAwards.html |archive-date=2018-05-28}}</ref> }}
